node.text: Who can’t wait for sp👀ky season?! 🙌👻🤫 To celebrate the release of @aquietplacemovie Part II on Digital & Blu-ray, we’ve rounded up the 9 most haunted places in California! Swipe to see some of our favorites & find the full list at our link-in-bio! #LABucketlist #Partner

node.text: Tag your yachting crew🛥🌴🗿 Party at Sea aboard your own private yacht for a day on this chic & vibey 59ft Tiki Boat with up to 12 friends! Discounted reservations are now available on Bucketlisters.com or link-in-bio to learn more! @losangelesbucketlist #boat #la #marinadelrey
